response.summary: ABC News is an Australian news website that provides up-to-date news coverage across various categories including politics, world events, business, sports, health, and entertainment. The site features a user-friendly navigation structure that allows users to access the latest news and personalized content.
keyContent: Just In: Latest breaking news updates.
For You: Personalized news stories tailored to user interests.
Politics: Coverage of political news and events in Australia and globally.
World: International news and updates on global events.
Business: News related to the economy, markets, and business developments.
Analysis: In-depth articles and opinion pieces on current issues.
Sport: Coverage of various sports events and news.
